title: Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description:
Description: An exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Locate and open a table containing highlight or map.
3. Attempt to export the data from the table.
OB: An exception is thrown when trying to export data from a table that contains highlight or map.
EB: No exception should be thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight or map.
SR:
1. Open the attached report.
2. Locate and open a table containing highlight or map.
3. Export the data from the table and verify that no exception is thrown.
